Grown-ups must own up to call the battle by its rightful name: Pandemic in child rearing.
Nelson Mandela once said: “Fools multiply when wise men are silent.” It urgently behoves all concerned authorities to let our judicious actions speak louder than our words. The Treasury CS last week announced that temporary Covid-19 tax reliefs will expire at the end of the year. Speaker gives IEBC leeway to prepare for and conduct a by-election following the death of MP Justus Murunga. Protesting learners said the student was attacked on Saturday morning while taking a bath just before the morning preps.